&lt;p&gt;There is the - IMHO excellent - &lt;a href="http://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html"&gt;User's Guide&lt;/a&gt; that lists and explains every single command and configuration option. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And of course, there is this FAQ site that provides answers to a lot of questions, often in the form of configuration snippets.&lt;/p&gt;

